tion responsive.</strong> Créez des réglages personnalisés pour les ordinateurs de bureau, les tablettes & mobiles en permutant entre les appareils.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-6.gif?rev=1608748\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-6.gif?rev=1608748\" alt=\"&lt;strong&gt;Revision History.&lt;/strong&gt; Switch between earlier versions of your page design, so your design process is backed up, every step of the way.\"></a><p><strong>Revision History.</strong> Switch between earlier versions of your page design, so your design process is backed up, every step of the way.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-7.gif?rev=1608748\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-7.gif?rev=1608748\" alt=\"&lt;strong&gt;Shape Divider.&lt;/strong&gt; Choose from a wide array of shape dividers and separate your sections in endless ways, that until now were simply not possible.\"></a><p><strong>Shape Divider.</strong> Choose from a wide array of shape dividers and separate your sections in endless ways, that until now were simply not possible.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17638:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">ELEMENTOR PRO TOTALLY BROKE MY SITES</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaimethornton\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/199e9ee88ca87d21778dca8b396f07e3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/199e9ee88ca87d21778dca8b396f07e3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaimethornton\" class=\"reviewer-name\">JAIME THORNTON <small>(jaimethornton)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had been using the free version for about 2 years, I loved it and it really allowed to create freely. About a month ago I bought the PRO version and it all went downhill since... I make changes that aren\'t saved correctly by the plugin, resizing on mobile and tablet doesn\'t work and WORST OF ALL there is NO SUPPORT from the Elementor team... no way to talk to a person... Oh well, there is if you haven\'t bought it yet, pre-sales chat... I FEEL CHEATED!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Worldclass, best plugin so far</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mark080959\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/243d30b14c70d239f0615ef1b2a7fe1d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/243d30b14c70d239f0615ef1b2a7fe1d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mark080959\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mark080959</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I never never never write reviews for wp plugins. Because, honestly they are seldom better then average.  And if, companies ask outrageous prices, much more than the value. I found e.g. Divi such a thing. It looked nice, so i bought it, once using it, it seems to have been built by a non wordpress user. But this, ELEMENTOR, is wonderful. And everything works great without hesitation. It is so good, that i break my habit not to write reviews. I never saw such a value for money plugin, really. My compliments to the developers. So please keep making more of these kind of great tools. The theme builder is also a great thing the logic of reusing templates again wherever you want, saves a lot of time. I didnt find a way yet to have a way to implement templates in another site export and then import or so. Hope it is there or please put it on the wish list. Great layout, great tool!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">monster level customization</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atta98\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/57d5df9d9f2da3291bc514c9c7da4449?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/57d5df9d9f2da3291bc514c9c7da4449?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atta98\" class=\"reviewer-name\">atta98</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You are the best each day working with elemntor I love it more and more</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Almost perfect</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amarria\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9a8076bf27c709c14b1d2a9c30e6af6a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9a8076bf27c709c14b1d2a9c30e6af6a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amarria\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Amarria <small>(amarria)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Lets face it, this last update has been a travesty. However, it is clear that the team has been working hard to fix things and it is appreciated\n\nYou are almost there Elementor team. The last update 3.0.7 had no issues for me and I am now updating all my sites.\n\nKeep up the good work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Tried others, always came back.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allthebugsandmore\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec0cdbb3fd88a8354708cb28be6c3758?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec0cdbb3fd88a8354708cb28be6c3758?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allthebugsandmore\" class=\"reviewer-name\">allthebugsandmore</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Elementor is simply my favourite tool in the WP box.\nWhat you can do - even with the free version - is remarkable.\nI have a media design background and back then, when I initially got my hands on Elementor, it had me produce my first usable designs in no time. The UI is quite intuitive to use and delivers fast.\n \nIf I had to name disadvantages regarding Elementor, \nthey would be technical and not just Elementor related:\n<ol>\n<li>the produced code volume compared to manual coding</li>\n<li>the resulting amount of DOM levels</li>\n<li>the fact that I can\'t deactivate the advertised PRO elements in the free version, as well as any other third party element i wouldn\'t use in a given project, in order to eventually reduce the resulting whole code volume of a project</li>\n<li>the thing that the Elementor ecosystem (like many others) doesn\'t load just what it needs on a given page</li>\n<li>the tendency of add-on coders to make use of external resources that can not easly be bypassed or deactivated, as using third party resources could lead to trouble when working within the restrictions of the GDPR</li>\n</ol>\n\nAnd yes I know, some add-on coders allow single element deactivations. \nI also agree, that a free version means the folks who made them have a good right to advertise their buyable product too.\nAnd finally I also know for sure, that all these \"nice to haves\" are not at all an Elementor-only problem.\n\nConclusion: \ni recommend to give Elementor a try, if you haven\'t already!\n\nPS: I\'ve read a lot of the critical comments regarding the update to v3.x and the inefficient support even for Pro users.\nI guess, I was simply lucky up until now... (fingers crossed)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">wonderful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sjologo\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e6cb6dfe6f90f1709e478e61f34cf86?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e6cb6dfe6f90f1709e478e61f34cf86?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sjologo\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sjologo</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The best plugin to buld your site. Thank you</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">big pile of shit</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seoinhead\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0149db0978654450eb92e0f68488f41?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0149db0978654450eb92e0f68488f41?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seoinhead\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Yury <small>(seoinhead)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">After updating ver3 elements became a big pile of shit. Wasted time and money.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Brokenmentor</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dvdgp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18b6cbb2bacc309edc54e70731be3192?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18b6cbb2bacc309edc54e70731be3192?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dvdgp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dvdgp</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This makes creating websites more exciting, as you go to bed with some colors and functionalities in your page and, when you wake up, they may or may not have changed by themselves.\n\n3.x is a mess, it just doesn\'t work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I love Elementor!!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anastasioslalos\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3626f9a22a696776898cd69500426159?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3626f9a22a696776898cd69500426159?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anastasioslalos\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anastasioslalos</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Elementor is so simple that I save time, nerves and energy.\n\nThank you Elementor Team!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">From Gold to Dust</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/retaillabs\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3664cbba5d8fe100daaec1b10cfc691f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3664cbba5d8fe100daaec1b10cfc691f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/retaillabs\" class=\"reviewer-name\">retaillabs</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><strong>Elementor was the greatest thing to happen to WordPress for me.</strong> It changed the way I worked and gave me so much more freedom as a designer. That was until Version 3.0 was released.\n\n<strong>Version 3.0 of Elementor is without a doubt, the worst upgrade to any WordPress software I have ever experienced. </strong>Ever since it was released, I have spent weeks fixing broken sites and wasted days on trying to continue with building and editing existing builds only to end the day totally frustrated.\n\nAgain today, and after countless updates to both Elementor and Elementor Pro, an existing site needed modifications and I have spent several hours on what should have been 2 hours tops and I am still in frustration.\n\nIf you start a fresh build, Elementor  seems to be working now. But existing sites that have upgraded to V3.0, are complete disasters. I can not begin to tell you how many hours I have lost since it\'s release, and there is still no light at the end of the tunnel.\n\n<strong>Elementor should be providing all PRO users a free year or two for this absolute disaster</strong>, and even then it will not make up for the hours spent trying to fix everything that has and is still breaking. So bloody angry right now!\n</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:150:\"The most advanced frontend drag &amp; drop website builder. Create high-end, pixel perfect websites at record speeds. Any theme, any page, any design.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.3.0.7.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:149: