;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juhosistvan\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/89462cd5ed7b59f2143eb6757d83d441?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/89462cd5ed7b59f2143eb6757d83d441?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juhosistvan\" class=\"reviewer-name\">István <small>(juhosistvan)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 12, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A must have plugin for developers.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">We are so fortunate to have this plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rajivpro82\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/03145db1fcd5b6eb6fbbc11134419f30?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/03145db1fcd5b6eb6fbbc11134419f30?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rajivpro82\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rajiv.pro82</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You saved WordPress. Gutenberg editor is a pure, absolute and fresh piece of crap!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Righting the Gutenberg wrong!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/skidrow\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6995b6faa58799d0b60721e90b656ff2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6995b6faa58799d0b60721e90b656ff2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/skidrow\" class=\"reviewer-name\">skidrow <small>(Skidrow)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">From the minute I saw the Gutenberg editor I knew this was a SERIOUS mistake. Any software that is created/developed for use by end-users should have the demands and needs of these users at heart. The introduction of the Gutenberg editor showed the existence of an ulterior motive and/or agenda. Whoever of whatever the Gutenberg editor is meant for, it is not represented by the majority of the WordPress users. Fortunately, Jeff Starr comes to the rescue and rights a big wrong. Thanks a million, Jeff!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works as expected. Practical options.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ebbalena\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4a87c477ec8b5603369eaab216e3563?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4a87c477ec8b5603369eaab216e3563?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ebbalena\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ebbalena</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A practical and well working plugin. Thanks a lot!\n\nI especially like the possibility to select for which roles the plugin is to be activated. Maybe there could also be an individual setting level later on (that the administrator could disable Gutenberg only for some of the authors)?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Save lots of headaches!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daniel_word_press\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6c3279b07def14732a955f6c6747aa6c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6c3279b07def14732a955f6c6747aa6c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daniel_word_press\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Daniel <small>(daniel_word_press)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Fusion Builder button is not appearing in WordPress Avada theme? This plugin may help you!\n\nThank you for creating this awesome and useful plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The tool you need when you are a pro</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aglekis\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9aed4c3373374032e4ecdde02894d5fb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9aed4c3373374032e4ecdde02894d5fb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aglekis\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Gregoire Noyelle <small>(aglekis)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 24, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Gutenberg is not for pro website (wiht more control on design flow). So you need this plugin. \nThanks a lot Jeff </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:104:\"Disable Gutenberg Block Editor and restore the Classic Editor and original Edit Post screen (TinyMCE,…\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/disable-gutenberg.2.2.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70:\"https://ps.w.org/disable-gutenberg/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1925989\";s:7:\"caption\";s:48:\"Plugin Settings screen (showing default options)\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70:\"https://ps.w.org/disable-gutenberg/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1925989\";s:7:\"caption\";s:49:\"Plugin Settings screen (showing expanded options)\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:4:{s:12:\"block-editor\";s:12:\"block-editor\";s:14:\"classic-editor\";s:14:\"classic editor\";s:6:\"editor\";s:6:\"editor\";s:9:\"gutenberg\";s:9:\"gutenberg\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:17:{s:3:\"1.1\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/disable-gutenberg.1.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.2\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/disable-gutenberg.1.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/disable-gutenberg.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.1\";s:66:\"https://download