(442, '_site_transient_ddwplir-plinfo-kt-tinymce-color-grid', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":27:{s:4:\"name\";s:21:\"Central Color Palette\";s:4:\"slug\";s:21:\"kt-tinymce-color-grid\";s:7:\"version\";s:6:\"1.15.3\";s:6:\"author\";s:68:\"<a href=\"http://profiles.wordpress.org/kungtiger\">Daniel Menzies</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kungtiger\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:9:\"kungtiger\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kungtiger\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50918cc4a3c1bb8f7d9a2c9460a87bcc?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:15:\"Daniel Menȝies\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"5.2\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.3.4\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.3\";s:6:\"rating\";i:100;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:45;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:46;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:11;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:6;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:30000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2020-09-02 3:43pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-02-21\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:51:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/kt-tinymce-color-grid\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:2424:\"<p>Cette extension vous permet de gérer une palette de couleurs centrale sur tout le site pour un aspect uniforme. La palette du nouvel éditeur de blocs et de l’outil de personnalisation des thèmes sont pris en charge, ainsi que l’éditeur classique. Vous pouvez définir cette palette de couleurs centrale par le biais du menu des réglages. Toutes les extensions qui utilisent le sélecteur de couleurs de WordPress peuvent également bénéficier de cette extension.</p>\n<p>Cette extension prend en charge une installation multi-sites de WordPress.</p>\n<p>Also this plugin replaces the color picker for choosing a text or background color found inside the classic editor with a bigger and customizable color grid.</p>\n<p>For an easy migration between WordPress installations you can export and import your palette settings and colors.</p>\n<p><strong>Prise en charge de thèmes/extensions</strong><br />\nCentral Color Palette prend en charges ces extensions et thèmes :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.advancedcustomfields.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Advanced Custom Fields</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpastra.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Astra Theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Beaver Builder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/elementor\">Elementor 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://lcweb.it/fontpress\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FontPress</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://generatepress.com/premium\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">GeneratePress Premium</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hestia\">Thème Hestia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/neve\">Thème Neve</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.megamenu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Mega Max Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">OceanWP</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://oxygenbuilder.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Oxygen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wp-pagebuilderframework.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Page Builder Framework</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please not that Elementor 3 is currently <strong>not</strong> supported due to its new color management.</p>\n<h3>Documentation de l’API</h3>\n<p>Central Color Palette offers some methods, so have a look at the <a href=\"https://kungtiger.github.io/central-color-palette\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Documentation de l’API</a>.</p>\n<h3>Politique de confidentialité</h3>\n<p>Cette extension ne collecte ou n’utilise aucune donnée privée.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:1197:\"<p>Cette extension devrait fonctionner avec une installation standard de WordPress.</p>\n<p><strong>Recherche d’extension WordPress</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Allez dans votre WordPress et ouvrez <em>Extensions</em> &gt; <em>Ajouter une nouvelle</em></li>\n<li>Recherche pour <em>Central Color Palette</em></li>\n<li>Cliquez sur « Installer et activer l’extension »</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Dépôt des extensions WordPress</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Allez à <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/kt-tinymce-color-grid\">wordpress.org/plugins/kt-tinymce-color-grid</a> et téléchargez le zip</li>\n<li>Allez dans votre WordPress. Vous pouvez téléverser une extension via <code>/wp-admin/plugin-install.php?tab=upload</code></li>\n<li>Activatez l’extension via le menu <em>Extensions</em> dans WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Installation manuelle</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Allez à <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/kt-tinymce-color-grid\">wordpress.org/plugins/kt-tinymce-color-grid</a> et téléchargez le zip</li>\n<li>Upload the directory found inside the zip archive to your /wp-content/plugins/ directory</li>\n<li>Activatez l’extension via le menu <em>Extensions</em> dans WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:240:\"\n<h4>\nDes questions ? Des préoccupations ? Une demande de fonctionnalité ?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Veuillez <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/kt-tinymce-color-grid\">me contacter</a> et nous verrons ce que nous pouvons faire</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:8079:\"<h4>1.15.3</h4>\n<p>Fix: Broken palette integration for GeneratePress</p>\n<h4>1.15.2</h4>\n<p>Fix: per blog options overwrite each other in multisite setup</p>\n<h4>1.15.1</h4>\n<p>Fix: Broken version check for Elementor 2</p>\n<h4>1.15</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: WordPress multisite support</li>\n<li>Added: CSS variable names can now be set for each color</li>\n<li>Added: Color names as hover/title to OceanWP, Astra and GeneratePress color pickers</li>\n<li>Added: Selector to scope CSS variables can now be set for exports</li>\n<li>Added: Support for Oxygen Site Builder</li>\n<li>Fix: Untranslatable string</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.14.7</h4>\n<p>Added option to add global variables to the dashboard</p>\n<h4>1.14.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Transparency to Astra Theme</li>\n<li>Fix: Broken integration for Astra Theme</li>\n<li>Fix: broken integration for GeneratePress</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.14.5</h4>\n<p>Fix: Broken integration for Advanced Custom Fields (thanks to @webprom and @stk_jj)</p>\n<h4>1.14.4</h4>\n<p>Fix: Broken integration for Elementor 2.9 (thanks to @blackeye0013)</p>\n<h4>1.14.3</h4>\n<p>Fix: Missing percentage characters for HSL exports</p>\n<h4>1.14.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajouté : prise en charge du <a href=\"https://sukiwp.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">thème Suki</a></li>\n<li>Correctif : prise en charge du nouveau sélecteur de couleur d’Elementor</li>\n<li>Fixed: Broken sprintf for alpha checkboxes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.14.1</h4>\n<p>Added: Color formats to CSS/SCSS based exports</p>\n<h4>1.14</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajouté : prise en charge de <a href=\"https://www.advancedcustomfields.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Advanced Custom Fields</a></li>\n<li>Ajouté : prise en charge de <a href=\"https://www.megamenu.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Mega Max Menu</a></li>\n<li>Ajouté : option pour les variables CSS globales</li>\n<li>Ajouté : type d’export pour les variables CSS</li>\n<li>Ajouté : types de couleur</li>\n<li>Fix: CSS to match WP 5.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.11</h4>\n<p>Ajouté : prise en charge de FontPress</p>\n<h4>1.13.10</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: « Clear Color » cell to the picker of the classic editor when only using the palette</li>\n<li>Fix: Unset variable warning when saving an empty palette (thanks to @cadiz)</li>\n<li>Fix: Syntax error for older PHP versions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.9</h4>\n<p>Classic Editor: Added an option to add a missing « Clear Color » cell to the picker when only using the palette</p>\n<h4>1.13.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Elementor: Fixes broken alpha channel</li>\n<li>Elementor : ajoute le nom des couleurs au passage de la souris</li>\n<li>Correctif d’un bogue qui peut provoquer une erreur fatale sur les chargements de pages sans une instance WP_Screen</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Gutenberg: Fixed overwritten color classes on front-end (thanks to @t0b1hh)</li>\n<li>Elementor: Fixed palette size and row display for many colors (thanks to @stevewoody82)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.6</h4>\n<p>Correctif du téléversement/import cassé de palette</p>\n<h4>1.13.5</h4>\n<p>Fixed broken download for JSON and Backup formats</p>\n<h4>1.13.4</h4>\n<p>Fixed bug: new palette color are not save due to logic error</p>\n<h4>1.13.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajout de la prise en charge du thème Hestia</li>\n<li>Added public method to manually set the central palette (suggested by @mrhasbean)</li>\n<li>Fixed bug in color sanitation method</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Correctif d’incompatibilité avec Elementor Pro</li>\n<li>Ajout de la prise en charge du thème Neve</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed broken Import</li>\n<li>Fixed JavaScript bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.13</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Gutenberg/block editor support</li>\n<li>Transparency channel is now always visible inside the palette editor</li>\n<li>Transparency can now be toggled individually for those integrations that use it</li>\n<li>Les couleurs peuvent être désactivées pour les masquer dans l’éditeur de blocs mais conservent leur affectation sur un niveau de bloc</li>\n<li>Les imports tentent de réutiliser les couleurs existantes pour réduire le chaos dans l’éditeur de bloc</li>\n<li>Ajout de nouveaux formats d’export</li>\n<li>Ajout de l’import JSON</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.12.6</h4>\n<p>Customizer palette breaks into rows of 8 colors</p>\n<h4>1.12.5</h4>\n<p>Fixed faulty output on palette save (thanks to @cavalierlife)</p>\n<h4>1.12.4</h4>\n<p>Fixed unstable integration with Elementor (thanks to @eplanet)</p>\n<h4>1.12.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed dynamic styles interfering with other parts of TinyMCE (thanks to @jb2386)</li>\n<li>Added credits to changelog of all those who contributed</li>\n<li>Added GDPR notice to readme</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.12.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Clarified what « Add to Customizer » does</li>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://wpastra.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Astra Theme</a></li>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://wp-pagebuilderframework.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Page Builder Framework</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.12.1</h4>\n<p>Fixed a bug where opacity values are displayed instead of color names</p>\n<h4>1.12</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Beaver Builder</a></li>\n<li>Fixed some bugs and typos</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.11</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://oceanwp.org\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">OceanWP</a></li>\n<li>Fixed alpha picker for Chrome</li>\n<li>Removed palette import, it&rsquo;s to buggy.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.10</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/elementor\">Elementor</a> (thanks to @blackeye0013)</li>\n<li>Added support for <a href=\"https://generatepress.com/premium\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">GeneratePress Premium</a> (thanks to @eplanet)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.9.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed fatal error when updating from an older version than 1.6 (thanks to @flixflix)</li>\n<li>Removed dependancy on farbtastic; now the color picker ships self-contained</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.9.2</h4>\n<p>Corrected some palette import bugs</p>\n<h4>1.9.1</h4>\n<p>Fixed fatal error due to missing wp_is_mobile on network installations of WordPress (thanks to @kzeni)</p>\n<h4>1.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Import third party palettes</li>\n<li>Automatic color names thanks to Chirag Mehta&rsquo;s <a href=\"http://chir.ag/projects/ntc\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Name that Color</a> and @flixflix</li>\n<li>Improved backup</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>All settings and the palette can now be exported and imported (suggested by @sigersmit)</li>\n<li>Added new grid type: only central palette for TinyMCE (suggested by @jhned)</li>\n<li>Added CSS for right-to-left locales</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.7.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes JavaSript bug (thanks to @hrohh)</li>\n<li>Fixes conflict with Poedit (thanks to @hrohh)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.7.1</h4>\n<p>Corrected typos and some translation strings</p>\n<h4>1.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Theme Customizer support added (thanks to @kzeni)</li>\n<li>Color grid is now adjustable in type and size</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.6.1</h4>\n<p>Fixed hidden colors after defining more than 13 colors (thanks to @wlashack)</p>\n<h4>1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Useability improvements</li>\n<li>Faster grid generation by using pre-calculated colors</li>\n<li>Namespaced CSS IDs and HTML form variables to avoid name collisions</li>\n<li>Fixed CSS errors</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.5</h4>\n<p>Added clean uninstall routine</p>\n<h4>1.4.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed possible JavaScript error</li>\n<li>Reduced overhead</li>\n<li>Removed language files; now handled by GlotPress</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.3</h4>\n<p>Update for WordPress 4.4</p>\n<h4>1.4.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Repaired headers already send error</li>\n<li>Preparation for GlotPress</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.1</h4>\n<p>Fixed a broken script</p>\n<h4>1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Improved settings page</li>\n<li>Improved accessibility</li>\n<li>Fixed security leaks</li>\n<li>Fixed translation bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.1</h4>\n<p>Changed HTML to conform with WordPress 4.3</p>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<p>Added support for custom persistent colors (thanks to @cash3p)</p>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<p>Fixes an error when using more than one TinyMCE</p>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Stylesheet gets enqueued only on pages with a TinyMCE</li>\n<li>Reduced overhead</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<p>Version initiale.</p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1169:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2369273\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2369273\" alt=\"L’éditeur de palette de couleurs\"></a><p>L’éditeur de palette de couleurs</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2207621\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2207621\" alt=\"Le nouvel éditeur de bloc est pris en charge\"></a><p>Le nouvel éditeur de bloc est pris en charge</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2003539\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2003539\" alt=\"Personnaliser la palette de l’outil de personnalisation du thème\"></a><p>Personnaliser la palette de l’outil de personnalisation du thème</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2003539\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/kt-tinymce-color-grid/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2003539\" alt=\"Legacy support for the classic editor\"></a><p>Legacy support for the classic editor</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14935:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">integration with kadence theme</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atelieruldeweb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/314494dbc4cfa64e2842c8b4b97d4b75?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/314494dbc4cfa64e2842c8b4b97d4b75?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atelieruldeweb\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Calin MANESCU <small>(atelieruldeweb)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">hello daniel!\nyour plugin is awesome!\ndo you plan to implement support for the most praised theme of the day: Kadence?\nthanks!\ncalin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Most Awesome Plugin for Design</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sberman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b6a6ab5bdcefd2d22ffc0f56963b8d2f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b6a6ab5bdcefd2d22ffc0f56963b8d2f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sberman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sberman</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is one of the best plugins for design! Wish I had discovered it 5 websites ago. It instantly changed all color palettes and save me tons of time. Worked with Gutenburg and my theme. Haven\'t tried it with Classic Editor yet. LOVE LOVE LOVE it so far. Hopefully it will continue to serve well. If so, I am adding it to my master \"must have\" plugins list. THANK YOU to the developer!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Time &amp; Life Saver!!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/uomomacchina\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73f8aeb52144b68f41b63f5c0e937453?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73f8aeb52144b68f41b63f5c0e937453?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/uomomacchina\" class=\"reviewer-name\">UomoMacchina</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 31, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The best Color Palette customizer for Gutenberg (and Classic Editor).\nGreat UI design, awesome features.\n\nI hope the developer add also the ability to show in the backend editor also custom color applied by <em><strong>custom CSS Classe</strong></em> to <strong>HTML Tags</strong> (i.e. I use 3 different classes to customize &lt;mark&gt; tag, but I can see them only in frontend and it will be useful if they will be visible in Gutenberg paragraphs.\n\nThank you so much for coding and sharing this wonderful plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Limited Elementor Compatibility</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ahmetsali\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9da5cf8ee0674b4c83956be7722cf78c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9da5cf8ee0674b4c83956be7722cf78c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ahmetsali\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ahmetsali</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">unfortunately changing current colors from plugin settings doesn\'t update the colors used in the elementor widgets.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solid Plugin, Quick Fixes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/roadsunknown\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/36c15042122f9f881878510c45dbffc8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/36c15042122f9f881878510c45dbffc8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/roadsunknown\" class=\"reviewer-name\">roadsunknown</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 18, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great compatibility with Wordpress, popular themes, builders, etc. When an integration broke after a theme update, the developer quickly fixed and published. Amazing!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great for custom Gutenberg color palettes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/computerbuddha\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/392e33c6471e5628d91ff996673370f1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/392e33c6471e5628d91ff996673370f1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/computerbuddha\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Computerbuddha</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is very useful to create custom color palettes for the Gutenberg editor and also the customizer. Works even with GeneratePress Premium. Thank you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Most useful plugin in the world</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/naomiblindeman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ac04bb9fcd3da2be49a3bee4034cc52?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ac04bb9fcd3da2be49a3bee4034cc52?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/naomiblindeman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Naomi Blindeman <small>(naomiblindeman)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 19, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is one of the first plugins I install on every single website I build. It makes developing sites easier and I know when I hand it over to my clients it will be so much easier for them to use their brand colors. The amount of hassle this plugin eliminates is delicious.\nSuch a simple concept, such a radical improvement!\n❤❤❤❤</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lovely! Should go into core</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martinsauter\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a3dfd2118c4292681000d1b9c99b0f6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a3dfd2118c4292681000d1b9c99b0f6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martinsauter\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Martin Sauter <small>(martin.sauter)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">décembre 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin makes it easy to create websites with consistent, tasteful colors. Something like this should be a standard feature in WordPress. As long as it\'s not, use this handy plugin. Highly recommended!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Just amazing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davelo\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9d135d7e82dd4e0473ee0a960f432298?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9d135d7e82dd4e0473ee0a960f432298?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davelo\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dave Loodts <small>(davelo)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you Daniel for creating this amazing plugin.\nThe brand new CSS variable totally rocks! Just so easy to have colour management on one place.\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ahorra tiempo</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/javiguion\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ba7d960c90f80b4142fb357cd81f499?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ba7d960c90f80b4142fb357cd81f499?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\