e\">Unused CSS Wonderchild!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shirtguy72\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d64efbbbf3d1c2c733eecfc878626c3a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d64efbbbf3d1c2c733eecfc878626c3a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shirtguy72\" class=\"reviewer-name\">shirtguy72</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 19, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Wonderfully lightweight and useful plugin, much thanks!  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A Must for All Developers&#039; Tool Kit</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/agentbey\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfd4de327db2bb5359e85b8e0a0d0cdb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfd4de327db2bb5359e85b8e0a0d0cdb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/agentbey\" class=\"reviewer-name\">agentbey</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is a simple tool that speeds up my web dev workflow. I use it for all my  site build projects. Highly recommend it!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">One of the first things I install</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scott_redletter\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3667fed8a0f6ca50eead77b68c4cbd6c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3667fed8a0f6ca50eead77b68c4cbd6c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scott_redletter\" class=\"reviewer-name\">scott_redletter</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">As soon as I start a site, I install this plugin right away. Simple - but effective.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome CSS Plugin! Keep updated time to time</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/biswas87\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5d50fd8e5f3da9d4817ce948dd5d5fcb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5d50fd8e5f3da9d4817ce948dd5d5fcb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/biswas87\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tanmoy Biswas <small>(biswas87)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Awesome CSS Plugin! Keep updated time to time. So Thanks again  \n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic plugin, great work! This is a must-download for every site.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/a305587\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f6ce4d0220733a66620fdf454794f135?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f6ce4d0220733a66620fdf454794f135?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/a305587\" class=\"reviewer-name\">a305587</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 7, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is one of those automatic plugins we add to every website we build. Our favorite feature is the ability to add (separately) both global and page-level CSS.\n\nIf you install this and it doesn\'t work, you probably just need to add \"!important;\" to the end of your CSS code.\n\nGreat work Tom, thank you for putting together such a great plugin for the WordPress community.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Did not work</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sonjarobertson\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/de0e255b73eaa820d870a55c879db32e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/de0e255b73eaa820d870a55c879db32e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sonjarobertson\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sonjarobertson</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 8, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I installed/activated the plugin and I pasted the font code in both the simple CSS box in the appearance-customize route, and I also pasted the code in the individual post. It didn\'t do anything! Am I doing something incorrectly? I need help and wasn\'t sure how to reach you, Tom, except by writing a review. I am very new to WordPress so it is quite possible I am doing something wrong on my end, and your plugin is not the issue because I\'m seeing so many 5 star reviews. Thanks for understanding.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple, fast and straight forward</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsl225\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/23779d0cabb343c05d867c49be7fd678?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/23779d0cabb343c05d867c49be7fd678?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsl225\" class=\"reviewer-name\">John <small>(dsl225)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and effective</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dfel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7de3d618f6db85a4c0dd3438096176ba?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7de3d618f6db85a4c0dd3438096176ba?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dfel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dfel</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Love the plugin, so clean &amp; easy to use, then again I wouldnt expect anything less from Tom! thanks for the great work</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:83:\"Add CSS to your website through an admin editor, the Customizer or a metabox for…\";s:13