org/builder-shortcode-extras/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=2154229\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;For Astra Pro: Shortcode for each Astra Custom Layout - great for reusage&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>For Astra Pro: Shortcode for each Astra Custom Layout - great for reusage</p></p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:1485:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good shortcode plug-in</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robobito\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f2b019f7ab363125ca19bea6fb730c5b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f2b019f7ab363125ca19bea6fb730c5b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robobito\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Quique <small>(Robobito)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It makes it very easy to do, I like the \"Last Updated Date/ Time\" shortcode very much. On the edit page the \"Shortcode for Reusable Blocks\" loads faster than if you use \"reusable blocks\".\nVery practical and useful.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:89:\"A collection of totally useful extra Shortcodes to make the life of Site Builders more…\";s:13:\"downl