(452, '_site_transient_ddwplir-plinfo-customizer-search', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":27:{s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Customizer Search\";s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"customizer-search\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.6\";s:6:\"author\";s:63:\"<a href=\"https://www.brainstormforce.com/\">Brainstorm Force</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nikschavan\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:2:{s:15:\"brainstormforce\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:46:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brainstormforce\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f4255d653745eaa037105cd5eab2295?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Brainstorm Force\";}s:10:\"nikschavan\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nikschavan\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0c22f3d5af6b870d815f66cf6216fa6e?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:13:\"Nikhil Chavan\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.5.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:6:\"rating\";i:100;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:8;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:8;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:40000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2020-08-21 12:42pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2017-07-31\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:47:\"https://github.com/Nikschavan/customizer-search\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:623:\"<p>Using a theme powered by the WordPress Customizer? Then you will love this plugin. Save the time and frustration finding options. Simply search for the setting you&rsquo;re looking for and get there instantly.</p>\n<p>Works with all WordPress themes.</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/IBFfap_vGzg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:323:\"<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/customizer-search</code> directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &lsquo;Plugins&rsquo; screen in WordPress</li>\n<li>Search field will appear when in the customizer.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1200:\"<h4>1.1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Admin notice CSS console error in admin area.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Fixed compatibility with other plugins with respect to the admin notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Users can now share non-personal usage data to help us test and develop better products. ( https://store.brainstormforce.com/usage-tracking/?utm_source=wp_dashboard&amp;utm_medium=general_settings&amp;utm_campaign=usage_tracking )</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Setup plugin translations through https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/customizer-search/.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Change the background color highlight in the searched results.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Highlight the characters that are matched in the results.</li>\n<li>Auto focus the search input when the search icon is clicked.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Rewrite the search logic to improve the search results.</li>\n<li>The search results are direct links to the customizer panel where the searched setting resides, This improves the required clicks to get to the search setting from old version.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:375:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1832749\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1832749\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1832749\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1832749\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:11840:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rubenvankempen\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b97a2488133dbaa930d12c44f4e24c29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b97a2488133dbaa930d12c44f4e24c29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rubenvankempen\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ruben <small>(rubenvankempen)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works perfect :D</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Really useful, one of the must-use plugins</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kwbtdisk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/373480d59170ef3212fa5c57036fe3d8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/373480d59170ef3212fa5c57036fe3d8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kwbtdisk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Daisuke Kawbata <small>(kwbtdisk)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 25, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you the BrainstormForce team! Great idea and high-quality works. I feel like it should include in the core source :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Brilliant! :)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/snifflevalve\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cf6b5c1018858eaebf521ac7fccc6628?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cf6b5c1018858eaebf521ac7fccc6628?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/snifflevalve\" class=\"reviewer-name\">snifflevalve <small>(SniffleValve)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 5, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">What a handy addition to the Customizer! :)\n\nOne suggestion:\nIt would be even handier if the search was at the very top of the Customizer because as it is now, once you arrive at your searched location, you have to navigate back to the Customizer home to search again.\n\nCheers!\nLyle</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">What a great idea!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quantum_leap\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d921655b085c7244c49902d12d292ac8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d921655b085c7244c49902d12d292ac8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quantum_leap\" class=\"reviewer-name\">George <small>(quantum_leap)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 5, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Whaoo, I just tried your plugin, what a time saver! Thanks for sharing it, I  think I will be installing it on all my websites now!\n\nCan I suggest something? The search should always stay there regardless of how deep in the options the user is. Right now the back button needs to be clicked multiple times to get to the Customizer home page settings and search for something else.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Time-s</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stevepritchardwoodturning\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7eb2072659ddea2173b434c840e80e58?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7eb2072659ddea2173b434c840e80e58?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stevepritchardwoodturning\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stevepritchardwoodturning</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 4, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great little plugin. A huge timesaver over searching for something. Just helped me find the \"back to top button\" setting in Generatepress! Thanks!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Time saver!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/logologics\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae7786630464c634521ede65ba95597a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae7786630464c634521ede65ba95597a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/logologics\" class=\"reviewer-name\">LogoLogics</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 3, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Cool, saves a lot of time and works also with OceanWP theme!\n\nThanks,\nAnnie</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A must-have plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oceanwp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05f8d3fe2ccb6479bac14e4d40b406dd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05f8d3fe2ccb6479bac14e4d40b406dd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oceanwp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">oceanwp</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 3, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you for creating such a great plugin, work perfectly with OceanWP. A must-have for any themes :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Big time saver for such a small plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ver3\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95f38d0dc869f268e5fedeed67e3bf29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95f38d0dc869f268e5fedeed67e3bf29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ver3\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Verdi Heinz <small>(Ver3)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 5, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This will be a default plugin for all our projects.\n\nIn excellent themes like Astra colors, typography and layout are in sperate sections. This clear division is great to have, but can sometimes be a disadvantage when you only want to quickly change something like H1 colors and typography. Using this plugin you just type in H1 and you can very quickly change the settings. Naturally, there are many more examples.\n\nUntil the customizer settings have tabs at the top like Elementor but with \"General\", \"Style\" and \"Advanced\" (for example), I\'ll be using this plugin!\n</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:34:\"Search for settings in customizer.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.6.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70:\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1832749\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70:\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-search/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1832749\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}}s:4:\"tags\";a:2:{s:10:\"customizer\";s:10:\"customizer\";s:6:\"search\";s:6:\"search\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:9:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.5\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.6\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.1.1.6.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-search.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:37:\"https://www.paypal.me/BrainstormForce\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low