=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ericmulder\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ericmulder</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very easy to switch between themes without losing your settings!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fmarconi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea23f62dcdd04e2acc8591cc5edc8b83?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea23f62dcdd04e2acc8591cc5edc8b83?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fmarconi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fmarconi</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works perfectly, thanks! I would love a litlle techinical teaching on how does it works and how to do the thing manually</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It works</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vadimkuznetsov\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/06d371afc173f50a6cd3d6e46bd5a62c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/06d371afc173f50a6cd3d6e46bd5a62c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vadimkuznetsov\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vadimkuznetsov</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works great! Really helpfull for transfer customizer settings from dev to live version.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Worked Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sallywolleat\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/735899a3ce16487aa02ad2f0c25aebec?s=16&#038;d=monster