"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thank You!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joeeible\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5c09b2e518d27fc36d414f5d25f4e064?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5c09b2e518d27fc36d414f5d25f4e064?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joeeible\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Joe <small>(joeeible)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I spent hours customizing a site only to realize that I never applied the child theme. Installed <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/customizer-export-import/\">Customizer Export/Import</a> and five minutes later I was back in business.   </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">useful with stage and production installation</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/openmindculture\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/38135ffca342b815f27dda84599fc18b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/38135ffca342b815f27dda84599fc18b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/openmindculture\" class=\"reviewer-name\">openmindculture</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Customizer Export/Import is useful for us to test settings on a stage installation and transfer it to production without using any of the more complicated staging tools and services, also useful to backup your settings.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:59:\"Easily export or import your WordPress customizer settings!\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:67:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-export-import.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/customizer-export-import/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1049984\";s:7:\"caption\";s:37:\"The export/import customizer section.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:10:\"customizer\";s:10:\"customizer\";s:17:\"customizer-export\";s:17:\"customizer export\";s:17:\"customizer-import\";s:17:\"customizer import\";s:6:\"export\";s:6:\"export\";s:6:\"import\";s:6:\"import\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:11:{s:3:\"0.1\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-export-import.0.1.zip\";s:3:\"0.2\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-export-import.0.2.zip\";s:3:\"0.3\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/customizer-export-impor