es images, des liens d’affiliation, etc.</p>\n<p>De plus, vous pouvez afficher un modèle en fonction du rôle de l&rsquo;utilisateur.</p>\n<h4>Comment ça fonctionne ?</h4>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/2wG1Jb0B7T4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Créez une mise en page avec Elementor.</li>\n<li>Allez aux réglages de l’extension et sélectionnez un modèle Elementor dans la liste déroulante pour n&rsquo;importe quel rôle utilisateur.</li>\n<li>Enregistrez les réglages. C’est fini !</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Nos autres modules pour Elementor</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://powerpackelements.com/?utm_medium=dashboard-welcome&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=powerpack-elementor\" title=\"PowerPack for Elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PowerPack for Elementor</a> &#8211; Étendre Elementor avec plus de 50 widgets créatifs et construire de beaux sites web.</p>\n<h3>Privacy Policy</h3>\n<p>Dashboard Welcome for Elementor uses <a href=\"https://appsero.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Appsero</a> SDK to collect some telemetry data upon user&rsquo;s confirmation. This helps us to troubleshoot problems faster &amp; make product improvements.</p>\n<p>Appsero SDK <strong>does not gather any data by default.</strong> The SDK only starts gathering basic telemetry data <strong>when a user allows it via the admin notice</strong>. We collect the data to ensure a great user experience for all our users.</p>\n<p>Integrating Appsero SDK <strong>DOES NOT IMMEDIATELY</strong> start gathering data, <strong>without confirmation from users in any case.</strong></p>\n<p>Learn more about how <a href=\"https://appsero.com/privacy-policy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Appsero collects and uses this data</a>.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:233:\"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Installez Dashboard Welcome via le répertoire des extensions WordPress ou en téléchargeant les fichiers sur votre serveur dans le dossier /wp-content/plugins/.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Activer l’extension.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:354:\"\n<h4>Quelles sont les conditions requises pour utiliser Dashboard Welcome ?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>L’extension Elementor doit être installée et activée pour que Dashboard Welcome fonctionne.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Ai-je besoin d’expérience en codage pour utiliser Dashboard Welcome ?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Pas du tout<! Tout ce que vous devez savoir sur Elementor.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:928:\"<h4>1.0.5 &#8211; April 20, 2020</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested compatibility with latest versions of WP and Elementor</li>\n<li>Added logic for usage analytics</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4 &#8211; August 28, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: PHP error on plugin page when Elementor is not active in multisite network</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3 &#8211; August 17, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enhancement: Added an option in main site to hide DWE settings from subsites in multisite enviornment</li>\n<li>Fix: Templates data was not available on subsites in multisite environment</li>\n<li>Fix: Minor CSS issues</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2 &#8211; August 3, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: PHP fatal error on multisite environment</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1 &#8211; July 24, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Scroll bar issue</li>\n<li>Fix: Empty widget was showing when template is not selected for different user roles</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; July 17, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Première version</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:706:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1910134\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1910134\" alt=\"Tableau de bord d&#039;administration - Panneau de bienvenue personnalisé\"></a><p>Tableau de bord d\'administration - Panneau de bienvenue personnalisé</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1931462\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1931462\" alt=\"Réglages de l’extension - Réglages de Dashboard Welcome\"></a><p>Réglages de l’extension - Réglages de Dashboard Welcome</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14593:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atomicnicholas\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40925257ba8a18176138444b9998180a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40925257ba8a18176138444b9998180a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atomicnicholas\" class=\"reviewer-name\">atomicnicholas</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Admin dashboards have never looked so beautiful.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works better than expected</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taropaa\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c83856bfedcc8a3960316529ec0e3d1a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c83856bfedcc8a3960316529ec0e3d1a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taropaa\" class=\"reviewer-name\">taropaa</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 6, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It works amazingly on multisite. \nNot only that, but its super easy to create one default template that will be used across the entire network!\n\nVery well thought out</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great idea and execution</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/john_pixle\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d73040e02178d44d394f5df0890ba796?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d73040e02178d44d394f5df0890ba796?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/john_pixle\" class=\"reviewer-name\">John Fraskos <small>(john_pixle)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 8, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works and feels great, very handy for almost any project. Great work on this as well!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">AWESOME :O</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zenben\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c05c25965e1a00b43870591111d869d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c05c25965e1a00b43870591111d869d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zenben\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ZenBen</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 20, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello IdeaBox Creations,\nTHANK YOU for this plugin, it is insanely useful!\n\nWith much appreciation,\nBen</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very practical and useful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo-fr\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6528bd707bcfdb72ad4f14d5219c8ad?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6528bd707bcfdb72ad4f14d5219c8ad?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo-fr\" class=\"reviewer-name\">momo-fr</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 17, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use it for some time on several websites of customers to facilitate the management of their content and guide them daily. We can do everything we want with Elementor and it\'s magic!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin, very useful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/horizzons\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0794bfc2a9df80313a320b93f2dc75bc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0794bfc2a9df80313a320b93f2dc75bc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/horizzons\" class=\"reviewer-name\">horizzons</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 17, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Working perfect.\nThanks</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful, thanks!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alex-soundmaster\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/37aa46732566f1666ca7381b0ae3bcd0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/37aa46732566f1666ca7381b0ae3bcd0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alex-soundmaster\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Alex Soundmaster</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 24, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very useful, thanks! Great plugin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nullmem\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2964a3aeceb7834c9759325da075c537?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2964a3aeceb7834c9759325da075c537?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nullmem\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nullmem</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 24, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Cool idea for a plugin. Keep up the good work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chagassilva\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eeca5f765c7147bea2f3fa1e4a024bd4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eeca5f765c7147bea2f3fa1e4a024bd4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chagassilva\" class=\"reviewer-name\">chagassilva</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 21, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">another incredible plugin, from this incredible team.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I have ideas.. but thanks for this</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ianstudio\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1332161335645f39d22fc4decb2de70?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1332161335645f39d22fc4decb2de70?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ianstudio\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ianstudio</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 21, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hi, since Granular seems to be \"abandonware\", glad for this.\n\nMy feedback..\n\n1: In admin I think it should be under Elementor rather than under Settings..\n\n2: Would be good to be able to have an Edit button for the chosen template directly in the  settings page.\n\n3: I would see something where you could mix and match Elementor sections directly from the setting so you could almost \"build a page\" quickly that way..  and organize them by drag and drop (something that would look a bit like the Nested Pages plugin). Say you temporarily want to add some sort of info.. boom you created a section, then you add it to certain roles in between whatever section make up their panel and you\'re done.\n\n4: Don\'t know if you could add a Template Type, coud be named Dashboard (like we have Section etc..) in case one ends up having lots of them. Am thinking someone who created lots of user roles, some very specific.. also if one has lots of sections already saved (would keep things more organized, especially if you implemented 3), also the dropdown would then only show this Template Type...\n\n5: And you could even create ready made Dashboard Elements, stuff that has to do with server info, note taking etc.. along the lines of this:\nhttps://wordpress.org/plugins/dashboard-widgets-suite/\n\nOk I\'m taking this too far :0)\n\nI loooove backend tools !!!!!!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:100:\"Remplace le panneau d’accueil par défaut du tableau de bord WordPress par un modèle Elementor…\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:74:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1910134\";s:7:\"caption\";s:69:\"Tableau de bord d\'administration - Panneau de bienvenue personnalisé\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1931462\";s:7:\"caption\";s:59:\"Réglages de l’extension - Réglages de Dashboard Welcome\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:17:\"dashboard-welcome\";s:17:\"dashboard welcome\";s:16:\"dashboard-widget\";s:16:\"dashboard widget\";s:9:\"elementor\";s:9:\"elementor\";s:15:\"elementor-addon\";s:15:\"elementor addon\";s:18:\"elementor-template\";s:18:\"elementor template\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:5:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor.1.0.4.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=1910112\";s:4:\"high\";b:0;}s:5:\"icons\";a:2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/icon-128x128.png?rev=1910112\";s:2:\"2x\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/dashboard-welcome-for-elementor/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=1910112\";}}', 'no'),
