href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/televizor\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/79bc911c2bb9a2eb985cd147445700e5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/79bc911c2bb9a2eb985cd147445700e5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/televizor\" class=\"reviewer-name\">televizor</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 23, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you for your work. This actually saved my life.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Experienced Multiple Issues from this Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aylward709\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/227b187393b8c78c8121241dec7d7dd1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/227b187393b8c78c8121241dec7d7dd1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aylward709\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aylward709</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 31, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I experienced 2 different issues on 2 different websites, both were caused by this plugin. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">0 Zero. Not good for free users.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/smallprogrammers\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c8944bb2ab9fc21aa3080c46754ff18c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c8944bb2ab9fc21aa3080c46754ff18c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/smallprogrammers\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Akib <small>(smallprogrammers)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was download the plugin to see huge downloads and 5 star.But after install it...i got frustrated.\nUseless plugin. You can use it on your way untill you pay for premium.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect, but needs only one BIG thing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shamiam1980\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2334a8b55680de6ab4e46874168847d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2334a8b55680de6ab4e46874168847d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shamiam1980\" class=\"reviewer-name\">shamiam1980</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">décembre 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A perfect simple functional plugin, which lacks only one big thing; Indentation and maybe some JS braces coloring</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">AMAZING !!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aledigitale\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e9589c1163e764ef52d9e2d1d2e29de9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e9589c1163e764ef52d9e2d1d2e29de9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aledigitale\" class=\"reviewer-name\">A.Digitale <small>(aledigitale)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">décembre 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin really rocks and works PERFECTLY and SMOOTHLY. Our entire Site relies 100% on it. This plugin injects JS and CSS \"on the fly\" on your WP pages and works like a charm! Simple and really efficient UI. Really a must-have for every developer.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A well thought out plugin that achieves exactly what it states</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/parasshah\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/697b7065f51617e491072d74f8091225?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/697b7065f51617e491072d74f8091225?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/parasshah\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Paras Shah <small>(ParasShah)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The best part of this plugin is the ability to have different snippets of code in separate posts like structure. It helps to quickly identify the purpose of that code without having to go through the rest of it.\n\nPretty versatile with a lot of options for control over visibility. Great plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Waste of time</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cyclonetheme\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/069dcd4c64e1ae10a8a08e69896c71b5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/069dcd4c64e1ae10a8a08e69896c71b5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cyclonetheme\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Cyclone Themes <small>(cyclonetheme)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am an administrator but also I see this message.\n\nYou need a higher level of permission.\nSorry, you are not allowed to edit posts in this post type.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">WTF?</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/neuroticartist\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82dd540c06f7ab13f465574cc5ef62f3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82dd540c06f7ab13f465574cc5ef62f3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/neuroticartist\" class=\"reviewer-name\">neuroticartist</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 1, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using this plugin for forever, it was rock solid, even when it was left unattended and un-updated for several years. Now its got tons of crap in it, lots of grayed out areas and no revisions unless you go pro?\n\nThis was my go-to plugin. Simple, clean, perfect. Now it goes in the trash never to be used again. WTF? Why screw up a perfect thing? The author is clearly relying on years of 5-star reviews that have nothing to do with this new version. </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:67:\"Easily add Custom CSS or JS to your website with an awesome editor.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/custom-css-js.3.33.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/custom-css-js/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1770918\";s:7:\"caption\";s:26:\"<p>Manage Custom Codes</p>\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s: