(470, '_site_transient_ddwplir-plinfo-wpcore', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":27:{s:4:\"name\";s:21:\"WPCore Plugin Manager\";s:4:\"slug\";s:6:\"wpcore\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.9.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://stuey.net\">Stuart Starr</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stueynet\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:8:\"stueynet\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stueynet\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73cd8d8ce433649aa4490acaee0e4141?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:8:\"stueynet\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"3.5\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.5.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:6:\"rating\";i:96;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:22;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:1;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:24;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2020-08-01 12:17am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2014-07-13\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:18:\"https://wpcore.com\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:300:\"<p>WPCore is a tool that allows you to manage collections of WordPress plugins and then quickly install them on any WordPress site. You can generate your collections at https://wpcore.com and then import them to your WordPress site by copying and pasting your unique collection key in WordPress.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:563:\"<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin via https://wpcore.com/download.</li>\n<li>Upload the ZIP file through the \\ »Plugins &gt; Add New &gt; Upload\\ » screen in your WordPress dashboard.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the \\&rsquo;Plugins\\&rsquo; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Generate a plugin collection https://wpcore.com/collections/create</li>\n<li>Add some plugins to that collection</li>\n<li>Copy the unique collection key</li>\n<li>In your WordPress admin panel visit Settings -&gt; WPCore</li>\n<li>Add collection keys</li>\n<li>Install the plugins!</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:105:\"<p>You&rsquo;ll find the <a href=\"https://wpcore.com/help\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ on WPcore.com</a>.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:3438:\"<h4>1.9.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed calls to screen_icon</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.9.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added WP-CLI support!</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.8.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update textdomain so you see notices</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.8.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update textdomain so you see notices</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.8.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update to TGM plugin Activation version 2.6.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.7.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add ability to export all plugins in addition to active plugins</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.7.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update to version 2.5.2 of http://tgmpluginactivation.com/</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.6.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Remove wpcore_keys from options table upon plugin uninstall / delete</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.6.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor fix to ensure only users with the &lsquo;install_plugins&rsquo; capability can see it</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.6.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated the TGM activation class to 2.4.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.5.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix for error on php 5.3 and below</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Merged pull request from cfoellmann/fixes and updated some urls for https</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed conflict when other plugins or themes use the TGM activation plugin. The install plugins button always works now.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Export active plugins to a WPCore.com collection.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested on WordPress 3.9.2. Works!</li>\n<li>Added some more input sanity(ization)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Switched to ssl. Changed timeout.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Further optimization. Now only 1 API call is made for all your collections. Dramatic speed increase in when saving collection keys.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Increased cache timeout. Click clear cache button in settings to fetch latest collection info</li>\n<li>Tested with Multisite</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue where in some cases users were getting  Cannot redeclare wpcore_set_false()</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>MAJOR PERFORMANCE UPDATE!</li>\n<li>Completely restructured the plugin to use the WordPress transient cache</li>\n<li>Will only make external calls to WPCore API when you save and edit your collection keys</li>\n<li>Major speed improvement</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Reenabled the admin nag dismiss button.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated Plugin name to alleviate some confusion between this plugin and the WordPress Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed bug that caused all the assets on the WordPress.org SVN to go missing. All good now.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated readme again (sorry)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated readme again (sorry)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated readme</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete refactor. Adherence to all WP.org coding standards. More Object oriented.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Using wp_remote_get and wp_remote_retrieve_body to grab stuff from wpcore.com</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Organized the menu. Put it near plugins cause that just makes sense.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed warning for undefined variable</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>This is the first usable build</li>\n<li>Add and edit multiple keys</li>\n<li>Install tons of plugins all at once</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Hopefully fixed the changelog</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Nothing here either</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Not too much in this one</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First one</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:509:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=949029\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=949029\" alt=\"Create plugin collections at wpcore.com\"></a><p>Create plugin collections at wpcore.com</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=949029\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=949029\" alt=\"Install them instantly on any WordPress site.\"></a><p>Install them instantly on any WordPress site.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14413:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">incompatible w/ too many themes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nadworks\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f77910a92d4badb021168de1b65268db?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f77910a92d4badb021168de1b65268db?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nadworks\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nadworks</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A great idea, but sadly increasingly incompatible with too many themes. Most of my regular premium themes throw up 404 errors as soon as I hit \"install plugins\" from within WP Core. According to the plugin\'s support, there\'s \"unfortunately nothing that can be done\". \nToo bad.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bakari45\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95cf709739b1b294dc3a20fafe55f3b1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95cf709739b1b294dc3a20fafe55f3b1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bakari45\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Bakari Chavanu <small>(bakari45)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 31, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I’m surprised I never heard of this plugin before. It’s so useful, and it’s going to safe me time in setting up new sites. Thanks for keeping this plugin updated. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful to those who create many sites</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/samrods\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6f92e80ab2fccf76ea92955c88f9ac75?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6f92e80ab2fccf76ea92955c88f9ac75?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/samrods\" class=\"reviewer-name\">samrods</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Right now it is the very first plugin I install in every freseh wordpress install: it stores all my favorite essentials plugins so i save precious time installing them one by one.\nThanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great but difficult to find on the search page</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/argdev\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/faefef07936ac939979ed3ed85622738?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/faefef07936ac939979ed3ed85622738?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/argdev\" class=\"reviewer-name\">argdev</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 22, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hey, amazing plugin! Congratulations.\n\nOne minor but sometimes annoying thing is that is difficult to find from the Install new plugin page in the Wordpress panel. Often I forget that is WPCore and I search wp-core, wp core, wpcore, Wp core and alike and I can\'t find it until I Google it and get it right.\n\nThanks for the plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muy útil</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ramallogg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39cc1552afc0cbb5a004c4364456ed76?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39cc1552afc0cbb5a004c4364456ed76?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ramallogg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ramallogg</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 4, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Ahorra un montón de tiempo al tener todos los plugins en un solo plugin. Fantástico. Recomendado. Solo hay que crear una cuenta en el sitio del creador. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Forced me to create an account on their website</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allkaiser\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62092d032d962eb2fd92331bc39e202b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62092d032d962eb2fd92331bc39e202b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allkaiser\" class=\"reviewer-name\">allkaiser</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 5, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I really just wanted a plugin that I could use to install a list of plugins. This made me create a whole account on their website, etc. A rather annoying and roundabout process.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Extremely useful plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pagelab\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88699017cad694da9222c6fd18d84a8f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88699017cad694da9222c6fd18d84a8f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pagelab\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Marcio Duarte <small>(pagelab)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 20, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I find it helps a lot in situations where you need to install and activate lots of plugins at the same time.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Incredible time saver</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukascech\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfd6da57d5ed117bbc03e336f8d288e8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfd6da57d5ed117bbc03e336f8d288e8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukascech\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lukascech</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 28, 2016</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This works perfectly, saves time and you don\'t have to remember all the plugins you like to use :).\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent and Easy to use. A Real Time Saver!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mizunga\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ac51e0e0d266d1bff62c74a097f1277e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ac51e0e0d266d1bff62c74a097f1277e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mizunga\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mizunga</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 3, 2016</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><p>It makes the process of installing plugins much easier and faster. It is a must for agencies, developers or designers.\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quantum-leap\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a67da749e0cfc839c376c8b7dd3d8836?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a67da749e0cfc839c376c8b7dd3d8836?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quantum-leap\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Kristof Loyens Quantum Leap <small>(Quantum Leap)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 3, 2016</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Installed on every site i use. Download all plugins i need for a site from my own set of plugins. Easy install. Saves me a lot of time.\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:78:\"Create plugin collections and install them in one click on any WordPress site.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:49:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wpcore.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:58:\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=949029\";s:7:\"caption\";s:39:\"Create plugin collections at wpcore.com\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:58:\"https://ps.w.org/wpcore/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=949029\";s:7:\"caption\";s:45:\"Install them instantly on any WordPress site.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:5:\"admin\";s