/75141ebb795716dc28f15e50edace13d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/greggwatson\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Artfuldodger <small>(gregg.watson)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Fantastic plugin. This is saving our dev team countless hours by letting us customize the Elementor Builder UI, best feature...hmmm well being able to right click and collapse or expand all widget elements and also the ability to drag and resize the widget grid.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:144:\"The plugin &quot;Flexible Elementor Panel&quot; makes the Elementor editor panel flexible, draggable, resizable, folding and more opportunities.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/flexible-elementor-panel.2.2.2.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:8:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:44:\"Panneau Elementor coulissant n’importe où\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:28:\"Exit button in editor footer\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:30:\"More skin for Elementor editor\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-4.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:27:\"Panneau Elementor repliable\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-5.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:32:\"More options for responsive mode\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/flexible-elementor-panel/assets/screenshot-6.gif?rev=2252139\";s:7:\"caption\";s:34:\"Flex and Sortable widgets category\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3