ful, well-conceived plugin. Comes with a variety of highly customizable blocks.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Kadence, you really seam to be the best block kit !</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ishko\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f46ca248c2944ca421331c78f390b5a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f46ca248c2944ca421331c78f390b5a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ishko\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ishko</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">After testing several other block kits plugins, I definitely adopt Kadence (free version, at this time) !\nSettings are numerous and useful. Very complete. Love the gallery settings, advanced buttons and the way columns are managed.\nI was afraid that my clients would change to much things and break the pages with such a tool but the option to select default settings for each block types and/or disable access to some settings for non admins achieved to seduce me.\nThanks for this awesome tool !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"re