n class=\"review-date\">août 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you for building this plugin and providing this great functionality!  \nI am especially grateful for the responsive settings for my blocks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muy buen Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artdesignnetwork\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3769ec21cc8b59224c83aa7894e69cc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3769ec21cc8b59224c83aa7894e69cc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artdesignnetwork\" class=\"reviewer-name\">artdesignnetwork</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Es un plugin que permite funciones especificas muy necesarias, excelente complemento para otros plugins.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">All Gutenberg needs</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martinsauter\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a3dfd2118c4292681000d1b9c99b0f6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a3dfd2118c4292681000d1b9c99b0f6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martinsauter\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Martin Sauter <small>(martin.sauter)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This powerful and clean plug-in adds many useful features to the block editor. As long as the official Gutenberg plug-in does not implement these features, EditorsKit is a great companion to Gutenberg.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fmarconi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea23f62dcdd04e2acc8591cc5edc8b83?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea23f62dcdd04e2acc8591cc5edc8b83?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fmarconi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fmarconi</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 16, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is very useful, and combined with Kadence Blocks is all you need. No more bloat page builders.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">All what I need</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larsvegas2\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ca20baa442b86faeed607b38ba28344?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ca20baa442b86faeed607b38ba28344?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larsvegas2\" class=\"reviewer-name\">larsvegas2</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am new to WP, but I am sure that too much plugin material is not a good way for my system. This is a part that I need and that works and is nice and clear.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Hide On Mobile Feature Is Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dharrshen\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fdec10044545f55719b079f3ed121fe4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fdec10044545f55719b079f3ed121fe4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dharrshen\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dharrshen</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s just all-around useful and it was great enough for me to create an account and leave a review &lt;3 </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A must for WordPress</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryanrainey\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc8a24ed25d69c56dae2432af88f8f4d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc8a24ed25d69c56dae2432af88f8f4d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryanrainey\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Bryan Rainey <small>(bryanrainey)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 2, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Unless you design every single page on your site with a page builder, EditorsKit is an absolute must!\n\nI love Gutenberg, but it lacks several important pieces (i.e. mobile response settings), which EditorsKit provides.\n\nDo yourself a favor and install EditorsKit. I promise, you\'ll be glad you did.\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">So Far So Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shahoud\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3012ec077b3c6683c3adcd1c8094bac?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3012ec077b3c6683c3adcd1c8094bac?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shahoud\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Joe Shahoud <small>(shahoud)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">So far the EditorsKit appears to be doing what its supposed to be doing. I really haven\'t had any problems and it gives me options I wouldn\'t normally have.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:102:\"EditorsKit fournit un ensemble d\'outils de construction de pages pour booster le nouvel éditeur de…\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:56:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/block-options.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:10:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-1.png?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:31:\"Couleurs de texte et surlignage\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-2.png?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:57:\"Formats de texte riche pour l\'éditeur de blocs Gutenberg\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-3.png?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:79:\"Visibilité selon les tailles d\'écran et l\'état de connexion des utilisateurs\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-4.png?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:19:\"Paramètres de bloc\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-5.gif?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:34:\"Styles de blocs Image et Bannière\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trunk/screenshot-6.png?rev=2362457\";s:7:\"caption\";s:22:\"Paramètres et options\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/block-options/trun