tar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/75b01acab5921ca64af0d307c1f2065a?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:6:\"pojosh\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.9\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.5.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.4\";s:6:\"rating\";i:100;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:8;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:8;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2020-09-03 12:34pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2018-10-15\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:90:\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=block-builder&utm_campaign=plugin-uri&utm_medium=wp-dash\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:2013:\"<p>Elementor Blocks for Gutenberg, officiellement créé par l’équipe <strong><a href=\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=block-builder&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">d’Elementor Page Builder</a></strong>, vous permet d’insérer facilement n’importe quel modèle Elementor dans Gutenberg en un seul clic.</p>\n<p>Cette extension est le moyen le plus intelligent de combiner Elementor &amp; Gutenberg pour incorporer des mises en page plus avancées dans Gutenberg.</p>\n<p>Elementor Blocks nécessite que Gutenberg &#038; Elementor soient actifs sur votre site (après la fusion de Gutenberg dans WordPress 5.0, seule une installation d’Elementor sera nécessaire).</p>\n<h4>Comment utiliser Elementor Blocks ?</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Installez &#038; activez Elementor Blocks for Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Dans la recherche Gutenberg pour « Bibliothèque Elementor »</li>\n<li>Choisissez un modèle existant ou créez-en un nouveau à partir de zéro</li>\n<li>Fini ! Maintenant vous pouvez voir le modèle Elementor que vous avez choisi prévisualisé à l’intérieur de Gutenberg.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Fonctionnalités</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Insérer des blocs et modèles Elementor dans n’importe quelle zone dans Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Prévisualiser le modèle directement dans l’éditeur Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Accès facile pour modifier n’importe quel modèle Elementor directement à partir de l’éditeur Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Choisir parmi plus de 300 blocs &#038; plus de 100 pages pré-conçues</li>\n<li>Personnaliser vos blocs Elementor avec des options de conception illimitées</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Compatible multilingue &#038; RTL</h4>\n<p>Nous avons intégré le support RTL et multilingue, ce qui vous permet d’obtenir un panneau traduit dès sa sortie, et vous pouvez même ajouter d’autres langues en allant à : <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/block-builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/block-builder</a></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:912:\"<h4>Prérequis minimum</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>La dernière version de l’extension Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Elementor version 2.2.0 ou supérieure</li>\n<li>PHP version 5.4 ou supérieure (PHP 7.2 ou supérieure est recommandé)</li>\n<li>MySQL version 5.6 ou supérieure</li>\n<li>Limite mémoire WordPress de 64 Mo ou plus (128 Mo ou plus est préférable)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Installez à l&rsquo;aide du programme d&rsquo;installation intégré d’extension de WordPress ou extrayez le fichier .zip et déposez le contenu dans le répertoire wp-content/plugins/ de votre installation WordPress.</li>\n<li>Activez l’extension via le menu « Extensions » dans WordPress</li>\n<li>Allez dans Gutenberg > Ajouter un nouveau bloc</li>\n<li>Choisissez le bloc de la bibliothèque Elementor</li>\n<li>Vous pouvez maintenant choisir un modèle dans la liste à l’intérieur de la zone de contenu</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:398:\"\n<h4>\nComment utiliser Elementor Blocks ?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Installez &#038; activez Elementor Blocks for Gutenberg</li>\n<li>Dans la recherche Gutenberg pour « Bibliothèque Elementor »</li>\n<li>Choisissez un modèle existant ou créez-en un nouveau à partir de zéro</li>\n<li>Terminé ! Vous pouvez maintenant voir le modèle Elementor que vous avez choisi dans Gutenberg</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:299:\"<h4>1.0.1 &#8211; 2018-11-06</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajustement : Ajout de la compatibilité pour WordPress v5.0 Beta (<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/compatibility-with-wordpress-5-0-beta-1/\">Sujet</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; 2018-10-15</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Version publique initiale</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:963:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1956874\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1956874\" alt=\"Ajouter un bloc de bibliothèque Elementor à l’intérieur de Gutenberg\"></a><p>Ajouter un bloc de bibliothèque Elementor à l’intérieur de Gutenberg</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1956874\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1956874\" alt=\"Bloc de bibliothèque Elementor avec prévisualisation d’un modèle\"></a><p>Bloc de bibliothèque Elementor avec prévisualisation d’un modèle</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=1956874\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=1956874\" alt=\"Ajout d’un bloc de la bibliothèque Elementor dans Gutenberg\"></a><p>Ajout d’un bloc de la bibliothèque Elementor dans Gutenberg</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:11444:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A must have for Elementor!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adminkhaled\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7da5e34f32023766948bb6ff9d5a6061?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7da5e34f32023766948bb6ff9d5a6061?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adminkhaled\" class=\"reviewer-name\">DJ Khaled <small>(adminkhaled)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin allows your Elementor  elements to be used in Gutenberg. You click the Elementor block, choose your global element from the dropdown, and voila.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Absolutely Essential</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/philrp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02d209c849f99ea725d334cb8439db83?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02d209c849f99ea725d334cb8439db83?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/philrp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">philrp</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is absolutely essential to have, as it permits the use of Gutenberg while maintaining the Elementor styling and design flexibility.\n\nWhen other plugins are not fully integrated with Elementor, it permits the use of Elementor blocks one what is a standard WordPress page. My use case: membership plugins.\n\n<strong>Please ensure compatibility with Wordpress 5.5</strong>\n\nThank you Elementor</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kbam\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50d7feae888551c4dff8cd6df4559a41?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50d7feae888551c4dff8cd6df4559a41?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kbam\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kbam</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use the plugin a lot and I\'m happy so far. However, I\'m waiting for Wordpress 5.5 compatibility. When are you releasing an update?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">High quality</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/release737\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b51b658fa9c8378d16cd15ee452391d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b51b658fa9c8378d16cd15ee452391d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/release737\" class=\"reviewer-name\">release737</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This website has high quality for using</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very nice blocks</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/billymiligan567\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bcd1d92ad7445c198a9242c562d713d9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bcd1d92ad7445c198a9242c562d713d9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/billymiligan567\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Billy Miligan <small>(billymiligan567)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juin 1, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">So helpful and easy to use blocks! Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/smitpatadiya\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e1e37992804e5400b137dedca47ba13a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e1e37992804e5400b137dedca47ba13a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/smitpatadiya\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Smit Patadiya <small>(smitpatadiya)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 1, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Saved my weeks for building a website.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Really nice plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larygejyds21\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa82343a11321b352598ece80c93366f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa82343a11321b352598ece80c93366f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larygejyds21\" class=\"reviewer-name\">larygejyds21</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 31, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you very much for really nice blocks plugins! Very helpful tool!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Elementor elements in Gutenberg</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/llis\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69822c3628946c4502e1cca2b2e8b4ca?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69822c3628946c4502e1cca2b2e8b4ca?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/llis\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Laura Scott <small>(llis)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 17, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This module makes your saved Elementor global elements available in Gutenberg. You click the Elementor block, then select your global element from the dropdown.\n\nI hope crossover ends up easier down the line, but that\'s not really Elementor\'s fault. Architecturally, Elementor is like on the other side of a brick wall from Gutenberg. And as long as Gutenberg remains the bleeding-edge content composer, I\'m just glad to be able to pull some of my Elementor goodness into a basic page.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:136:\"Elementor Blocks for Gutenberg, officiellement créé par l’équipe d’Elementor Page Builder, vous permet d’insérer facilement…\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/block-builder.1.0.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1956874\";s:7:\"caption\";s:73:\"Ajouter un bloc de bibliothèque Elementor à l’intérieur de Gutenberg\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1956874\";s:7:\"caption\";s:69:\"Bloc de bibliothèque Elementor avec prévisualisation d’un modèle\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=1956874\";s:7:\"caption\";s:62:\"Ajout d’un bloc de la bibliothèque Elementor dans Gutenberg\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:5:\"block\";s:5:\"block\";s:13:\"block-builder\";s:13:\"Block Builder\";s:6:\"design\";s:6:\"design\";s:9:\"elementor\";s:9:\"elementor\";s:9:\"gutenberg\";s:9:\"gutenberg\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:3:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/block-builder.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/block-builder.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:56:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/block-builder.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:68:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=1956874\";s:4:\"high\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/banner-1544x500.png?rev=1956874\";}s:5:\"icons\";a:2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/icon-128x128.png?rev=1956874\";s:2:\"2x\";s:66:\"https://ps.w.org/block-builder/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=1956874\";}}', 'no'),
